description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News & ParaShare Hospital Horrors: Ghosts of the ER Edition

Dave & Tim are admitted to a Hospital of Horrors as we explore creepy hospital paranormal encounters plus we report on Supernatural News from around the world, a UFO near collision with an airplane, paranormal investigators uncover human remains during an investigation, worrisome Weather Control news PLUS a Brand New Theater of the Mind and your emails!

Watch the newest episode of Holzer Files, Ancient Evil with Darkness Dave NOW on Discovery+
